Package cs213.photoAlbum.model

Interface Summary
BackendInterface This interface is used to store and fetch User data.
 

Class Summary
Album The Album class contains:
- Unique album name
- The name of the user the album belongs to
- An Array List containing photos
Backend The backend class is responsible for storing and fetching User data.
Photo The Photo class contains:
- Unique file name
- Name of the user photo belongs to
- Caption
- Timestamp
Tag The tag object is used to represent an appearnce of a location or a person or common things in multiple photos.
User The User class contains the information relating to a single user.
